{"tid":3473,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本最可愛小學生是她！天使萌眼網友「心被奪走了」","createTime":"2016-11-26T07:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T13:16:50.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe85f97303a65f0820348fed2908e19fad4bef6","tid":3473,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T07:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2171/d2171592.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2171%2Fd2171592.jpg&h=4e74cbf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲元倉燈擊敗3000多個小朋友，成為「日本最可愛小學生」冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n日本繼推出「千年一遇女偶像」、「最可愛高中生」後，又出現「日本最可愛小學生」元倉燈（元倉あかり）。現年8歲的她就讀小學2年級，擔任雜誌《小學一年生》的專屬模特兒1年多，近日接下食品廣告成為話題，超萌大眼加上天真無邪的笑顏，馬上掀起網友熱烈討論。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2171/d2171593.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2171%2Fd2171593.jpg&h=82decb69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元倉燈在2014年參加選秀活動，擊敗3000多名競爭者脫穎而出，被封為「全日本最可愛的小學生」。而她面對大批鎂光燈仍保持滿面笑容，並說：「我平常在家裡玩，最喜歡跟弟弟在床上睡覺」、「最喜歡的科目就是不出作業的科目」，童言童語萌翻全場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CjFgiJQVEAArMZX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCjFgiJQVEAArMZX.jpg&h=19d8396c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友大讚8歲的元倉燈超可愛，直呼「我的心被奪走了」、「好像天使」，眾人稱讚小女孩的澄明大眼，期待將來長大會變成大美女。<br />\n<a href=\"http://star.ettoday.net/news/818266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F818266&d=WXy6%2FEefggLTTy5in0AyrsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=4919e553\" target=\"_blank\">http://star.ettoday.net/news/818266</a>"},{"pid":"378e975961061420509dd8d02cddfdc68a160722","tid":3473,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T07:18:01.000Z","msg":"可以下海拍野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b16a8e7305a6142e1dca82e3a5769f429fb3ef","tid":3473,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T07:20:12.000Z","